5:
So to recap: that room we just
visited is gonna be yours, Sotieth.
7:
It's probably missing a lot of
necessities, but don't worry. We'll
take you to Palpebra sometime
soon and pick up stuff while we
show you around.
15:
...Er, we don't HAVE to go soon
though. Whenever you feel ready
works for us.
19: Thank you. But I am... fine.
21:
Rashid entrusted me with an order. 
I will see it through.
36:
Thank you for saving us the other
day, Nephtim. I am Sotieth.
40:
Nephtim is Nephtim. You are Sotieth.
Acknowledged.
52: Yes... It appears I am your sister.
57: She is? Have you two met before?
60:
No. We exchanged data a moment
ago. It came to our attention that
she is a later model of my design.
63:
O-oh... So that's why she called you
her sister.
66:
...I was created to activate the Titan.
Surely Nephtim, as a later model,
was enhanced to serve that
purpose even more effectively.
68: What function does she serve here?
72:
She doesn't. At least, not any one in
particular.
76:
Nephtim is here to play. Hanging out
with everyone is Nephtim's job.
80:
Sometimes performing too. Always
with perfect moves. Nephtim is hella
lit. The bee's knees. Cat's pajamas.
Yay.
88:
Yeah, I can see how that'd be
confusing...
97: I am afraid I do not comprehend.
101:
Just... don't worry about it. You'll see
what she means eventually.
108:
Nephtim. I look forward to getting to
know you.
114:
Acknowledged. Nephtim also wishes
to know you, Sister.
119:
Well, Nephtim, we've still got a few
more places to show Sotieth. We'll
catch you later.
123:
Phew, that was a LOT of shopping.
That should be everything on the list.
126:
Sotieth, is there anything else you
wanted to grab?
129: Negative. There is nothing I need.
133:
Wait a moment. There is a note at
the end of the list.
137:
"For dinner, prepare Hamburg steaks
with decorative flags. Carrots are
unnecessary."
143:
That has got to be Nephtim's doing...
When did she manage to sneak that
in?
147:
It seems Nephtim and the others are
in town as well.
150:
They could've come over to say hi.
Wonder what's got them in such a
rush.
153: Eh, we can ask them about it later.
156:
For now, let's focus on grabbing the
necessary meat and carrots. We
can indulge her every once in a
while.
159:
Did she not write that the carrots
were unnecessary?
173:
Hamburg steaks are amazing. Very
delicious.
177: I agree. It was very good.
182: Ahaha, glad to hear you liked it.
185:
I am curious what the purpose of
the decorative flag was, though...
201:
Is this what you were out buying
earlier?
205:
Sure was... Got dragged around
everywhere for it.
209:
Eating delicious food and receiving
presents should improve one's
mood.
219: I feel... much better. Thank you.
224:
So that's what you were up to,
Nephtim...
228:
Don't worry, Sotieth. We've got plenty
more nice dinners to treat you to.
232:
The gesture is appreciated. Thank
you too.
